  http://cgi.din.or.jp/~tkent/tmp/zsh-3.0.0-os2-a01.zip

  This is zsh-3.0.0 OS/2 port, can do file-completion and
globbing in case-insensitive by "setopt ignorecases"

  There is another OS/2 port of zsh-3.1 which do
case-insensitive completion and globbing. But I forget its
location.

